The annual special 40 days and nights fasting and prayer programme of Celestial Church of Christ (CCC), Coconut Parish, which kicked off January 5, will be rounded off on February 13, 2022. The programme with the theme, ‘He Is God’, has been held at Ogudu – Ori-Oke road, Ogudu, Ojota, Lagos. The initiator, Prophet Michael Olabode, also known as Success, said: “There are a lot of benefits for attendees, including salvation, deliverance, healing, among others,” even as he urged people with a myriad of problems to embrace the programme.